i>CML transforming into <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"9ab5f0308116927771814e1fcc72d6\">AML</span> <strong>(Option B)</strong></li>\n<li>Occurs in an average of 3 years after the diagnosis of CML.</li>\n<li>Blasts on the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"5b9831f3aa169277718395d7361df6\">bone marrow</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"754ab07a2e1692777183ed178c883d\">biopsy</span> <strong>>20%.</strong></li>\n<li>Presence of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"0ba1f7edfa1692777187ae6f51e603\">extramedullary</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"42eb51d31e1692777183d170489ba8\">blastic</span> infiltrates.</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
